<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%- site.businessName %> — Employment Law Specialists</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Jost:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>

  <%- include('partials/header') %>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <span class="hero-tag">Employment Law Specialists</span>
      <h1>Employment advocates you can <em>rely on</em></h1>
      <p><%- site.businessName %> provides clear, practical employment law guidance to help you understand your rights at work. We take the complexity out of employment disputes so you can move forward with confidence.</p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Book a consultation</a>
        <a href="#services" class="btn-outline">Our services</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ABOUT -->
  <section class="about" id="about">
    <div class="about-inner">
      <div class="about-image"><span>Image placeholder</span></div>
      <div class="about-content">
        <span class="section-label">About us</span>
        <h2>Employment advocates dedicated to your rights</h2>
        <p><%- site.businessName %> is a team of employment law specialists committed to helping individuals navigate workplace disputes and understand their rights. We bring deep knowledge of employment law and genuine care for our clients' wellbeing.</p>
        <p>We believe employment disputes shouldn't be complicated. That's why we take the time to understand your situation and provide advice that is clear, practical, and focused on achieving the best possible outcome for you.</p>
        <div class="about-stats">
          <div>
            <span class="stat-num">200+</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Cases resolved</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="stat-num">$5M+</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Recovered for clients</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="stat-num">99%</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Client satisfaction</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SERVICES -->
  <section class="services" id="services">
    <div class="services-inner">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-label">What we do</span>
        <h2>Employment issues we can help with</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="services-grid">

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 11l3 3L22 4"/><path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h11"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Unfair Dismissal</h3>
          <p>If you've been dismissed unfairly, we help you understand your rights and take action to seek compensation.</p>
          <a href="/services/unfair-dismissal" class="service-link">Learn more</a>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm0 18c-4.42 0-8-3.58-8-8s3.58-8 8-8 8 3.58 8 8-3.58 8-8 8zm-1-13h2v6h-2zm0 8h2v2h-2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Workplace Bullying</h3>
          <p>Workplace bullying is serious. We help you document, report, and pursue action against bullying behaviour.</p>
          <a href="/services/workplace-bullying" class="service-link">Learn more</a>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Workplace Discrimination</h3>
          <p>Workplace Discrimination is unlawful. We support you with confidentiality and discretion to take action.</p>
          <a href="/services/sexual-harassment" class="service-link">Learn more</a>
        </div>

        <div class="service-card">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v16a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Personal Grievance</h3>
          <p>We help you raise formal personal grievances and represent you through mediation and dispute resolution.</p>
          <a href="/services/personal-grievance" class="service-link">Learn more</a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>

  <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
